== 争议 ==
2006年1月24日，均年仅18岁的Alexander Ryzanov与Wang-Piao Dumani Ross各自驾驶一辆[[梅赛德斯-奔驰|梅赛德斯-奔驰]]於[[多伦多|多伦多]]街头非法竞速，其中一人撞上一台[[出租车|出租车]]，并且肇事逃逸，导致46岁的出租车[[司机|司机]]Tahir Khan死亡<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/memorial-held-for-cab-driver-killed-in-alleged-street-race-1.584852 |title=Memorial held for cab driver killed in alleged street race |access-date=2017-12-27 |archive-date=2021-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314130945/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/memorial-held-for-cab-driver-killed-in-alleged-street-race-1.584852 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。鉴识人员事后於肇事车辆上发现一份《极品飞车》系列游戏之拷贝。有关该系列游戏过程中超速驾驶和逃避法律责任之问题遂开始引起社会关注。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news2/background/crime/street-racing.html |title=http://www.cbc.ca/news2/background/crime/street-racing.html Street Racing: Too fast, too furious |access-date=2017-12-27 |archive-date=2021-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314130950/https://www.cbc.ca/news2/background/crime/street-racing.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

